Package com.k3xs.JHamTune

Interface Summary
JHTRadio an interface implemented by drivers for each JHamTune supported radio.
 

Class Summary
JHamTune Top frame of JHamTune: contains menus, manages frequency data, builds other components.
JHTBand Encapsulates a frequency or frequency range and operating/modulation modes.
JHTCTCSS encapsulates CTCSS (Motorola PL tones) as a typesafe enum.
JHTMode Encapsulates modulation modes.
JHTModeCombo  
JHTScanBank Scans a bank of channels represented as JHTBand objects.
JHTSweepFrame Implements a graphic representation of a band segment, showing a histogram of signal strengths at various frequencies.
JHTSweepPanel GUI for band-sweeping.
JHTuner GUI for tuner.
SimulatedJHTRadio JHamTune driver for a simulated radio.
YaesuFT847 JHamTune driver for the Yaesu FT-847 radio.
